00:05:50.899 --> 00:05:55.899
So yes, Joseph recognized it was Jehovah who rewarded him.

00:05:55.899 --> 00:05:59.899
But Joseph's example can help us if we had a difficult childhood.

00:05:59.899 --> 00:06:04.899
