00:06:04.899 --> 00:06:07.899
We can stay contented and we can persevere.

00:06:07.899 --> 00:06:10.899
If we do, Jehovah will reward us now and in the future.

00:06:10.899 --> 00:06:13.899
The key is to remain faithful.

